[
  {
    "startTime": 0.0,
    "endTime": 2.544,
    "text": "- My family's much like anybody else's."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 2.544,
    "endTime": 3.377,
    "text": "- Mmhmm."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 3.377,
    "endTime": 8.1,
    "text": "There's half of them that you love and respect, and then, there's the other half."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 8.1,
    "endTime": 9.346,
    "text": "Which half am I meeting?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 9.346,
    "endTime": 10.25,
    "text": "(upbeat music)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 10.25,
    "endTime": 11.083,
    "text": "(punching)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 11.083,
    "endTime": 12.376,
    "text": "(screams)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 12.376,
    "endTime": 16.863,
    "text": "[Henry] Well, there's my cousin, Alistair, based in Taiwan, works in movies."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 16.863,
    "endTime": 18.012,
    "text": "(punching and screaming)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 18.012,
    "endTime": 18.903,
    "text": "[Director] Cut!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 18.903,
    "endTime": 19.849,
    "text": "(alarm goes off)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 19.85,
    "endTime": 22.703000000000003,
    "text": "[Henry] He's dating Kitty Pong, an actress."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 22.703,
    "endTime": 23.797,
    "text": "(claps)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 23.797,
    "endTime": 26.841,
    "text": "(upbeat tango music)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 26.841,
    "endTime": 28.1,
    "text": "[Kitty] Ah, you like it?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 28.1,
    "endTime": 30.458000000000002,
    "text": "I was feeling very, very..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 30.458,
    "endTime": 31.386999999999997,
    "text": "The emotions..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 31.388,
    "endTime": 32.940000000000005,
    "text": "Can you feel it?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 32.94,
    "endTime": 35.903,
    "text": "Oh, I can feel all of you, and all of me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 37.285,
    "endTime": 41.035,
    "text": "[Speaking Mandarin] She's terrible, can't we get someone else?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43.183,
    "endTime": 46.933,
    "text": "[Speaking Mandarin] He's financing the whole movie. You tell him his girlfriend sucks."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 49.74,
    "endTime": 52.75,
    "text": "Okay, and what about your cousin, Eddie, you don't ever talk about him."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 52.75,
    "endTime": 54.804,
    "text": "Well, Eddie's a big finance guy in Hong Kong."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 54.804,
    "endTime": 56.192,
    "text": "A real family man."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 56.192,
    "endTime": 57.922,
    "text": "(upbeat music)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 57.922,
    "endTime": 60.0,
    "text": "(camera shoots)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 60.0,
    "endTime": 62.37,
    "text": "[Russell] You know if you move, it would look more natural."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 62.37,
    "endTime": 64.95,
    "text": "No, this way you get our optimal angles."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 64.95,
    "endTime": 66.77,
    "text": "Ah, then we're done."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 68.545,
    "endTime": 70.31,
    "text": "Russell, thank you so much."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 70.31,
    "endTime": 72.36,
    "text": "It's an honor to be photographed by you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 72.36,
    "endTime": 75.85,
    "text": "My pleasure, people will love it in the next Hong Kong Vogue."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 75.85,
    "endTime": 76.85,
    "text": "Thank you, Russell."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 78.55,
    "endTime": 79.42,
    "text": "Hong Kong Vogue?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 79.42,
    "endTime": 81.41,
    "text": "I knew it, your dress is a disaster."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 81.41,
    "endTime": 84.39999999999999,
    "text": "If you wore a Bottega gown, like I told you to, we'd be in the American Vogue."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 84.4,
    "endTime": 86.807,
    "text": "You can wear that gown to hell, Eddie."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 86.807,
    "endTime": 88.69,
    "text": "(children's cars hoot)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 88.69,
    "endTime": 89.523,
    "text": "[Henry] And there's Astrid."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 89.523,
    "endTime": 91.759,
    "text": "Oh, I remember Astrid."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 91.76,
    "endTime": 93.80000000000001,
    "text": "She's like who I wanna be when I grow up."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 93.8,
    "endTime": 100.31099999999999,
    "text": "Astrid is awesome, and she's probably the only one I'm actually close with, and she's really grounded, and down-to-earth once you get to know her."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 100.311,
    "endTime": 103.061,
    "text": "(big band music)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.68,
    "endTime": 117.86000000000001,
    "text": "Not only did she graduate top of her class at Oxford, start multiple charities and is a fashion icon, Astrid has the biggest heart of any of my cousins."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 119.298,
    "endTime": 120.0,
    "text": "[Little Girl] Mummy, see what I made for bunny..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 120.0,
    "endTime": 122.029,
    "text": "No, not now."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 128.35,
    "endTime": 130.102,
    "text": "Hi, I'm Astrid."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 130.103,
    "endTime": 131.359,
    "text": "What's your name?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 131.359,
    "endTime": 132.842,
    "text": "[Little Girl] Ira."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 132.842,
    "endTime": 134.42800000000003,
    "text": "[Astrid] And who is this?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 134.428,
    "endTime": 135.261,
    "text": "Bunbun."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 136.34,
    "endTime": 140.345,
    "text": "Well, I think Bunbun looks very dashing with his bow."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 140.345,
    "endTime": 141.6,
    "text": "You have a good eye."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 141.6,
    "endTime": 142.73,
    "text": "Thank you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 142.73,
    "endTime": 145.14,
    "text": "[Man] Miss Leong, right this way."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 145.14,
    "endTime": 146.88,
    "text": "Very nice to meet you both."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 155.485,
    "endTime": 156.5,
    "text": "(door slams)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 156.5,
    "endTime": 159.29,
    "text": "[Jeweler] These are all brand new from Antwerp."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 159.29,
    "endTime": 161.44,
    "text": "You're the first person I've shown them to."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 166.39,
    "endTime": 167.506,
    "text": "What are those?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 168.998,
    "endTime": 169.831,
    "text": "Those?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 172.787,
    "endTime": 174.65300000000002,
    "text": "Those are very special."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 175.89,
    "endTime": 182.79199999999997,
    "text": "Burmese pearl drop earrings, set with emeralds and rare pigeon blood red rubies."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 182.793,
    "endTime": 188.56300000000002,
    "text": "They were worn by Queen Supayalat at her self-anointed coronation in 1878."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 190.01,
    "endTime": 190.843,
    "text": "How much?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 192.9,
    "endTime": 197.192,
    "text": "Having you wear one of my pieces is better publicity than I can buy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 198.66,
    "endTime": 199.953,
    "text": "I'll let them go at cost."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 201.6,
    "endTime": 203.01,
    "text": "1.2 million."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 204.82,
    "endTime": 207.82,
    "text": "(plane flies over)"
  }
]